{"tid":1013071,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"華人到宜家都係拜關公唔拜岳飛，證明哩個民族幾弱智","createTime":"2019-02-08T05:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T15:55:38.000Z","uid":57376,"like":72,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b2139741be7d82c628519ab28d79d760fb68e9","tid":1013071,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"明明係滿清狗為咗壓抑大漢主義先換咗關羽上去「武聖」個位，班漢人又真係戇鳩鳩咁集體轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家陣滿清都亡國百年啦，點解可以將錯就錯到宜家都唔改返？<br />\n支那就話因為畀共產黨愚民政策影響，咁香港華人呢？海外華人呢？個個都無讀歷史？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要得罪講句，關羽係中國歷代名將之中根本連條毛都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到戰功，項羽白起韓信霍去病之流贏佢九萬幾條街，要做「武聖」排隊都未到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條傻鳩仲要累到主公基業盡毀，放佢入名將之列都有辱其他人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲人會話關羽夠忠義，咁唔通岳飛會差得過佢？如果夠忠義就得咁就唔好叫「武聖」啦，叫「忠聖」好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本拜關公果班人都係無思考能力，隨波逐流，人拜佢又拜，是非不分，咁嘅弱智民族都想神仙保祐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486af0592282825c12f348de8ceead72512287c9","tid":1013071,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"唔係金人改嘅咩"},{"pid":"4a1ed221fb5a137856927d019f898f04646f5cb4","tid":1013071,"uid":98551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"Marketing 既重要性"},{"pid":"f9e554b33680c5e2b94eaae3fdde3425454e4903","tid":1013071,"uid":55493,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"仲要係拜民俗同文學層面嘅關羽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔定過多百幾年後人拜郭靖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef00117