 />\n不過本身個大佬都唔係好人😹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"跟著因爲諗起曹操以前俾女佢屌俾錢佢洗所以放佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果咁都叫忠義，應該無人唔忠義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7362e431397f542347fb53a7b4eeff478435e134","tid":1013071,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"邊個歷史人物最值得拜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5306426c52dd7bb2cd03b19995d2e314e925cd","tid":1013071,"uid":161781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"你都幾好野<br />\n明明喺第2個post就同你講得好清楚關羽信仰興喺清朝之前已經好興盛 而且官方地位都唔差過岳飛<br />\n咁都可以黎造謠"},{"pid":"680e95e7cfe48fffe734e7d0bca238d378a694c7","tid":1013071,"uid":42610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7362e431397f542347fb53a7b4eeff478435e134","tid":1013071,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"邊個歷史人物最值得拜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"明朝既于謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ec5fac4bbea141b55aa7c68c1833a7b7dd7bd1","tid":1013071,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7362e431397f542347fb53a7b4eeff478435e134","tid":1013071,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"邊個歷史人物最值得拜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"嫪毐"},{"pid":"10bdc6604f4ace41195be4c0d96b80e808480e95","tid":1013071,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98ec5fac4bbea141b55aa7c68c1833a7b7dd7bd1","tid":1013071,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7362e431397f542347fb53a7b4eeff478435e134","tid":1013071,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-0